{"tid":1490140,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"我真係唔知點解香港人到而家呢一刻仲對黑警咁仁慈","createTime":"2019-08-20T04:40:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T05:08:45.000Z","uid":36134,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a58dcea5e797194bcf12053990d5351c8c2aefa3","tid":1490140,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:40:03.000Z","msg":"黑警對付香港人既手段真係已經滅絕人性<br />\n佢地有幾多手足真係受傷入院？<br />\n我地手足比佢地虐打 施暴入院已經不計其數<br />\n<br />\n連入左院都唔放過<br />\n仲要縱容藍絲周街斬人<br />\n<br />\n根本同nazi縱容德國人虐待猶太人一撚樣<br />\n由佢地作為執法者對我地作出非人化描述個刻開始<br />\n佢地已經打算虐殺香港人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次唔搞掂同處理好黑警問題<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所有香港人以後要永遠承受黑警殘酷虐待</span></span>"},{"pid":"76d4b34b855f73ec20ad6a639bf78326699a6748","tid":1490140,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:41:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db461ed68d9f490b8cbc916cdf694c1d5ae3937d","tid":1490140,"uid":227381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:42:09.000Z","msg":"全民皆兵 刻不容緩"},{"pid":"f040a8446a0f969a2a06655d727bbf05846773e2","tid":1490140,"uid":49151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:43:40.000Z","msg":"因為有和理非"},{"pid":"10b2e3797ad1a8764e40a6835ba5b0d29f0e2f88","tid":1490140,"uid":215487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:46:01.000Z","msg":"我諗女仔比人拉到入去大獲 真係姦左都冇人知"},{"pid":"df7d40445b121109fb2ca1a4a5bdaeacc1764d9a","tid":1490140,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10b2e3797ad1a8764e40a6835ba5b0d29f0e2f88","tid":1490140,"uid":215487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:46:01.000Z","msg":"我諗女仔比人拉到入去大獲 真係姦左都冇人知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:07:39.000Z","msg":"唔係無試過"},{"pid":"e24010b2b112e1f5464f7e82458dd41b1d8b0eed","tid":1490140,"uid":215487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:08:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm